data.description: Discover the charm of this private retreat in the heart of Oklahoma's Green Country. Nestled on 2 acres of meticulously landscaped grounds, this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath ranch-style residence epitomizes serenity and comfort. Constructed in 1978, this home, which has been cherished by only two families, is now poised to become a part of your legacy. Updated throughout, the residence offers an ideal canvas for personalization, allowing you to infuse your unique style. The walkout basement utility room and a spacious two-car garage provide ample space for storage or the creation of a workshop tailored to your needs. The convenience of Adair school and seamless transfer options enhance the appeal of this property. Situated just minutes away from Adair, Pryor, and Claremore, with Grand Lake a short 30-minute drive and Tulsa accessible in 45 minutes via I-44 Turnpike, this location seamlessly balances tranquility with accessibility. Indulge in the unparalleled vistas from the rear deck, surrounded by the privacy afforded by mature trees that host a parade of wildlife. The property boasts pecans, walnuts, and occasional persimmon and chantrelle mushroom crops for foraging, adding a touch of rural charm. Witness deer grazing in the yard as you savor your morning coffee, or host a delightful barbecue on the kitchen-adjacent patio. Under the night sky, revel in the spectacle of stars, an increasingly rare sight. If your vision of a fulfilling life involves a tranquil haven enveloped by nature's beauty, complemented by the convenience of modern amenities, then this residence is poised to be your new home.
